#. type: Plain text
#: 2021-03-09-global-newsletter-49-1.md:299
msgid ""
"Who is Animal Rebellion? What is speciesism? Why is animal agriculture so "
"terrible? How can farmers transition away from it and still make a good "
"living? What would we do with all the empty fields? Should we all be vegan? "
